00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,820
>> Azure Advisor is
a free service built into Azure

2
00:00:02,820 --> 00:00:05,580
that provides recommendations
on high availability,

3
00:00:05,580 --> 00:00:09,030
security, performance, and cost.

4
00:00:09,030 --> 00:00:12,120
Advisor analyzes your deployed
services and looks for

5
00:00:12,120 --> 00:00:15,570
ways to improve your environment
across those four areas.

6
00:00:15,570 --> 00:00:19,570
With Azure Advisor, you can
get proactive, actionable,

7
00:00:19,570 --> 00:00:21,380
and personalized best practices and

8
00:00:21,380 --> 00:00:24,524
recommendations,
improved performance, security,

9
00:00:24,524 --> 00:00:26,595
and high availability
of your resources,

10
00:00:26,595 --> 00:00:30,175
and identify opportunities to
reduce your overall Azure costs,

11
00:00:30,175 --> 00:00:33,570
and get recommendations with
proposed actions inline.

12
00:00:33,570 --> 00:00:36,515
You can access Azure Advisor
through the Azure portal.

13
00:00:36,515 --> 00:00:38,165
After you sign into the portal,

14
00:00:38,165 --> 00:00:39,770
auto select "Advisor" from

15
00:00:39,770 --> 00:00:43,660
the "Navigation" menu or search
for it in the "All Services" menu.

16
00:00:43,660 --> 00:00:46,820
You can download recommendations
from Azure Advisor in

17
00:00:46,820 --> 00:00:50,200
PDF or CSV format, which
you can then share.

